パッケージ xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator

クラス Advancement

java.lang.Object
xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator.Advancement
public class Advancement extends Object
A configurable advancement which later may be saved to a file, loaded into the server. Visit this link for further information regarding advancements.

  • コンストラクタの詳細

    • Advancement

      public Advancement(org.bukkit.NamespacedKey id, ItemObject icon, net.md_5.bungee.api.chat.TextComponent title, net.md_5.bungee.api.chat.TextComponent description)
      Creates a new configurable advancement.
      パラメータ:
      id - the id of the advancement, this determines the file location and the in-game id
      icon - the item to display on the advancement screen. The root advancement's icon is the icon of the tab. The item property must be set before calling toJson(), the data property is optional
      title - the title of the advancement
      description - the description of the advancement

    • activate

      public static boolean activate(boolean reload, org.bukkit.NamespacedKey id, String json)
      Static method, useful when trying to activate a pre-generated (already JSON) advancement.
      パラメータ:
      reload - whether Bukkit.reloadData() should be called immediately after a file has been created. Calling that method only after all advancements have been activated is advised
      id - the id of the advancement
      json - the advancement in JSON format
      戻り値:
      whether the activation was successful

      public String toJson()
